 State University|Arizona State]]\n'''Youth'''\n*[[1981 Big League World Series|Big League World Series]]: [[Taipei, Taiwan]]\n*[[1981 Junior League World Series|Junior League World Series]]: [[Boardman, Ohio]]\n*[[1981 Little League World Series|Little League World Series]]: Tai-Ping, [[Taichung]], [[Taiwan]]\n*[[1981 Senior League World Series|Senior League World Series]]: [[Georgetown, Delaware]]\n\n==Awards and honors==\n*'''[[Baseball Hall of Fame]]'''\n**[[Rube Foster]]\n**[[Bob Gibson]]\n**[[Johnny Mize]]\n*'''[[MLB Most Valuable Player Award|Most Valuable Player]]'''\n**[[Rollie Fingers]], [[Milwaukee Brewers]], P (AL)\n**[[Mike Schmidt]], [[Philadelphia Phillies]], 3B (NL)\n*'''[[Cy Young Award]]'''\n**Rollie Fingers, Milwaukee Brewers (AL)\n**[[Fernando Valenzuela]], [[Los Angeles Dodgers]] (NL)\n*'''[[MLB Rookie of the Year Award|Rookie of the Year]]'''\n**[[Dave Righetti]], [[New York Yankees]], P (AL)\n**Fernando Valenzuela, Los Angeles Dodgers, P (NL)\n*'''[[Gold Glove Award]]'''\n**[[Mike Squires]] (1B) (AL) \n**[[Frank White (baseball)|Frank White]] (2B) (AL) \n**[[Buddy Bell]] (3B) (AL) \n**[[Alan Trammell]] (SS) (AL) \n**[[Dwight Evans (Baseball)|Dwight Evans]] (OF) (AL) \n**[[Rickey Henderson]] (OF) (AL) \n**[[Dwayne Murphy]] (OF) (AL)\n**[[Jim Sundberg]] (C) (AL) \n**[[Mike Norris (baseball)|Mike Norris]] (P) (AL)\n\n==MLB statistical leaders==\n{| cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"width:auto;font-size: 90%; border: 1px solid gray;\"\n|- align=\"center\" style=\"font-size: larger;\" \n| &nbsp;\n! colspan=2 | [[American League]]\n! colspan=2 | [[National League]]\n|- style=\"background:lightblue;\" \n! Type || Name || Stat || Name || Stat\n|- align=\"center\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" style=\"background:lightblue;\"\n|- \n| [[Batting average (baseball)|AVG]] || [[Carney Lansford]] BOS || .336 || [[Bill Madlock]] PIT || .341\n|-\n| [[Home run|HR]] || [[Tony Armas]] OAK<br>[[Dwight Evans (Baseball)|Dwight Evans]] BOS<br>[[Bobby Grich]] CAL<br>[[Eddi